---
title: Spring Greens Pesto Pizzas with Asparagus, Pancetta, and a Green Salad
description: Here’s a loaded flatbread that will take care of all of your pizza cravings without you ever having to reach for the phone. The flatbread crust is slathered with loads of herbaceous pesto as a base, then topped with crispy pancetta, asparagus, and mozzarella. There’s even a lemony side salad for good measure. (Pro tip: put some of the lettuce on your pizza for an amazing mash up of hot with cool ’n’ fresh.)
